---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contract Language Guide | Realtor Roof"
  description="Final contract inserts, PDF downloads, and copyable clauses are in legal review. We’ll notify you the moment they go live."
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-200 via-rose-200 to-orange-200 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-pink-300/50 via-transparent to-rose-400/40"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/60 bg-white/70 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 backdrop-blur">
        📋 Clauses & PDF Pack Under Review
      </span>
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
        Contract Language Guide Coming Soon
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-lg text-gray-700">
        Our real estate attorneys are finishing the buyer-protection clauses, addendum templates, and checklists you saw in the prototype. We’ll email the final PDF pack the moment it clears review.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/contact?topic=contract-guide"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 shadow-lg transition hover:bg-rose-50"
        >
          Reserve the PDF Pack
          <span>→</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/resources"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-white/60 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          Back to Resources
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-pink-100 text-xl">
            🛡️
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Buyer-Safe Language</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Pre-approved clauses that make Realtor Roof the default choice while keeping your contracts fully compliant.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-pink-100 text-xl">
            📂
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Editable Templates</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Addendum language, inspection response outlines, and task checklists formatted for Dotloop and SkySlope.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-pink-100 text-xl">
            ⚖️
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Attorney Reviewed</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Language vetted by Kansas real estate counsel so you can copy/paste with confidence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-pink-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-pink-100 text-xl">
            ⏱️
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Timeline Guidance</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Step-by-step instructions for negotiating repairs, scheduling work, and closing on time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
